            "OutBlock ch (e (p d)) # tr1m @ tr1'" d1 "\<lambda>_. State s2" "({}, {ch})" "InBlock ch v # tr2m' @ tr2'" tr']
            by auto
        qed
      qed
    qed
  next
    fix i cha vara p2 v tr2
    assume "i < length [(ch[!]e, C1)]" "[(ch[!]e, C1)] ! i = (cha[?]vara, p2)"
    then show ?thesis by simp
